@startuml Colaboracion-Basica-F8
title F8 - Colaboración básica en diseñador UML
autonumber

actor "Diseñador A" as A
actor "Diseñador B" as B
participant "Angular\nworkflow-designer" as UIA
participant "Angular\nworkflow-designer" as UIB
participant "WorkflowDesignerController" as WDC
participant "WorkflowCollaborationService" as WCS
database "workflow_collaboration" as DB
participant "BitacoraService" as BIT

== Apertura ==
A -> UIA : Abrir diseñador policyId
UIA -> WDC : POST .../collaboration/open
WDC -> WCS : registerOpen
WCS -> DB : sesión A
WCS -> BIT : WORKFLOW_ABIERTO

B -> UIB : Abrir mismo policyId
UIB -> WDC : POST .../collaboration/open
WDC -> WCS : registerOpen
WCS -> DB : sesión A + B

== Polling 11s ==
loop cada 11 segundos
  UIA -> WDC : GET .../collaboration?sessionId&baseRevision
  WDC -> WCS : heartbeat + stale check
  WCS --> UIA : connectedEditors, revision
end

== B modifica ==
B -> UIB : Guardar actividad
UIB -> WDC : POST /workflow-activities
note right: WorkflowActivityService\nregisterModification → revision++

== A detecta conflicto ==
UIA -> WDC : GET collaboration (baseRevision antigua)
WDC -> WCS : staleForClient = true
UIA --> A : Aviso conflicto\nbloqueo guardado
UIA -> WDC : POST .../collaboration/conflict
WCS -> BIT : CONFLICTO_EDICION

A -> UIA : Recargar diagrama
UIA -> WDC : GET designer + collaboration
note right: loadedRevision actualizada

@enduml
